Smile is written all over her face. The smile is backed by hope. Peninah Kitsao had "cooked" stone in the guise of food.
When we visited Ms Kitsao, she was moving into a newly-built six-bedroom house in Mtwapa, Kilifi County, courtesy of well-wishers.
As she carried her household items into the new house, that cost Sh1.4 million, Ms Kitsao could not hide her joy.



